DL_POLY is a parallel molecular dynamics simulation software developed
at Daresbury Laboratory by W. Smith, T.R. Forester and I.T. Todorov
under the auspices of the Science and Technology Facilities Council
(STFC) for the EPSRC's Collaborative Computational Project for the
Computer Simulation of Condensed Phases (CCP5) and the Computational
Science and Engineering Department (CSED) at Daresbury Laboratory.  The
software is the property of Science and Technology Facilities Council.
